       * <p>The agent will include runtime information, ex: <code>
       * Oracle-JavaSDK/1.0.0 (Linux/3.10.0-229.el7.x86_64; Java/1.8.0_60; Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM/25.60-b23)
